{
  "stem": "14613.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have seen, like from the cattle cars-- not only from ours, but there was a whole train of the cattle cars, everybody going out from the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have seen some-- in the cattle cars, you had a policeman who was a policeman in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were the people that I think were killed almost immediately by the-- by the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have seen, like, they would throw the policeman on the ground, beat him, stay on him, on his throat with their boots, until you could see the blood all over.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was the first picture of this killing, of these policemens coming out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then, really this is one of the times-- maybe the only time-- that I really lost completely control of-- of my movements, of my ability to think.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this is maybe the time where I became like a sheep in the flock, going with the crowd, without knowing what I am doing-- or unconsciously knowing what we doing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is a time when they separated us-- that means my brother and myself from my sisters and my mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is really the last time that we have seen them, until after the war where we met my two sisters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's no way-- there's no way to describe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no way to tell anyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no way to convey for the future the pain, the agony, the tragedy which was happening there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we went, my brother and I, in this long line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And wherever they told us, we went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just lost our sense of-- of freedoms, of anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And eventually, we-- we went to the bath house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took a shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
